reviews.text: It used to be my most-frequent visited place for dinner after work in last year. The beef brisket is OK but not great. After 2019 Chinese New Year, the price of basic bowl noodles is increased from HKD 28 to HKD 30. They also added MSG to the food and soup. 😓😞
Large variety of noodles to choose especially those of Chiu Chow atyle beef and fish ball noodles. Price is relatively cheap for locals.
My favorite food noodles  soup yummy 😋😋😋
Great food !
Good quality food
